<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/714210-for-a-first-read-is-the-abridged-version">For a first read, is the abridged version all right? Or should I go with the full version? Thanks!</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_714210'><a id="like_count_community_question_714210" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/714210?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">11 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F70561.The_Gulag_Archipelago_1918_1956">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/714210-for-a-first-read-is-the-abridged-version">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/714210-for-a-first-read-is-the-abridged-version">See all 5 answers</a>
